name: Proxy
description: Proxy Contract. NOTICE: Proxy must implement UpgradeableMaster interface to prevent calling some function of it not by master of proxy.

functionDecorators.name: getNoticePeriod
functionDecorators.description: UpgradeableMaster functionsNotice period before activation preparation status of upgrade mode.

functionDecorators.name: isReadyForUpgrade
functionDecorators.description: Checks that contract is ready for upgrade.

functionDecorators.name: transferMastership
functionDecorators.description: Transfer mastership of the contract to new master.

functionDecorators.name: upgradeCanceled
functionDecorators.description: Notifies proxy contract that upgrade canceled.

functionDecorators.name: upgradeFinishes
functionDecorators.description: Notifies proxy contract that upgrade finishes.

functionDecorators.name: upgradeNoticePeriodStarted
functionDecorators.description: Notifies proxy contract that notice period started.

functionDecorators.name: upgradePreparationStarted
functionDecorators.description: Notifies proxy contract that upgrade preparation status is activated.
